<h2>Tags</h2>
<p>Tags are used to indentify different transaction types (mortgage, utilites, etc.). Add as many, or as few, tags as you require.</p>
<p>Tempus sed tincidunt accumsan magna orci. Amet euismod aut accumsan a quis. A adipiscing auctor. A posuere nostra. Consequat est tortor feugiat a pharetra blandit turpis mauris a nec ut.</p>

<% if Tag.all().count() < 1 %>
  There current no tags registered to this app.
  <br/ >
  <a class="button" href="/tags/add">Add a Tag</a>
<% else %>
  <h3>Showing <%= Tag.all().count() %> tags</h3>
  <a class="button" href="/tags/add">Add a New Tag</a>
  <% @tags.each do |tag| %>
    <p class="display">
      Tag Name : <%= tag.tag_name %>
      <br />
      <a href="tags/<%= tag.id %>">View this Tag</a>
    </p>
  <% end %>
  <div class="changes">
    <a class="button" href="/tags/add">Add a New Tag</a>
  </div>
<% end %>
